highlights.text: “愛人錯過” by 告五人 has been on Viral Songs Vietnam the longest, at 241 days straight.
TimelessRemixes has the most spots on Viral Songs Vietnam. “Nhật ký tình đầu - Blues Rock” is the highest at #8.
“EM IS KITTY” by QuocKang, KHOA, and TTE Fast Considerate is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Vietnam, up 20 spots at #77.
“ĐÀ LẠT CÒN MƯA KHÔNG EM” by TRO-Music is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Vietnam at #1.
